items.title: Canal boats swallowed by giant hole as major incident declared
items.description: Two boats have been left at the bottom of the cavity, where water has drained away.

items.title: New Trump envoy says he will serve to make Greenland part of US
items.description: Denmark warns Washington to respect its sovereignty, while Greenland says it will decide its own future.

items.title: Zendaya and Tom Holland in surprise curry house stop
items.description: The famous couple turned up at the restaurant in Leicestershire while visiting the area to see a show.

items.title: Two identical Banksy murals appear in London
items.description: Banksy confirms a mural in Bayswater and is thought to be behind a second work in central London.

items.title: Russian general killed by car bomb in Moscow, officials say
items.description: Lt Gen Fanil Sarvarov is the third military official to have been killed in bomb attacks in the Russian capital over the last year.
